        "If you had not been a great host. I definitely had to struggle to finish the professional seminar that I attended in Perth, Australia. When I reached back to my place, I found that I left a very important file at your house, in the room I stayed in. I possibly kept it in the wooden cabinet I used, it is medium-size blue file holder made of plastic and has my name inscribed on it. I got an appreciation certificate in conference which is in the folder and want to shown in office to sanction my expenses.",
